          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1654602558649-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with the <strong>lime zest </strong>and<strong> </strong>the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Add<strong> half</strong> your <strong>honey </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> –<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>creamy lime dressing</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a little<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>cold water if the dressing is looking a little thick!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1654602565267-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
